ow</a>\n                 </td>\n      \n               </tr>\n             </table>\n           </td>\n         </tr>\n\t\t   \n\t\t   \n\t\t   \t\t   \t\t<tr>\n           <td width=\"100%\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#fff\" class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 32px 0px 0px 0px;\">\n             <table width=\"90%\" class=\"content\" style=\"border-spacing:0;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\" role=\"presentation\">\n               <tr>\n                 <td style=\"padding:16px; border-top: 1px solid #ccc; border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;\">\n                  <p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; Margin: 0;\"><q>The man who can see all gray, and red, and purples in a peach, will paint the peach rightly round, and rightly altogether.  But the man who has only studied its roundness may not see it's purples and grays, and if he does not will never get it to look like a peach; so that great power over colors is always a sign of large general art intellect.</q></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t   <p style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; Margin: 0;padding-top:7px;\">- John Ruskin</p>\n                 </td>\n               </tr>\n             </table>\n           </td>\n         </tr>\n\t\t   \n\t\t<tr>\n           <td width=\"100%\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#fff\" class=\"column\" style=\"padding: 16px 0px 0px 0px;\">\n             <table width=\"100%\" class=\"content\" style=\"border-spacing:0;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;\" role=\"presentation\">\n               <tr>\n\t           <td width=\"33%\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 0px 10px;\">\n                 <a href=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/barton_stone_hays_grapes_peaches_apple.html\" target=\"_blank\">\n                     <img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/dg6smdedp/image/upload/mailers/img/hays_grapes_apple.jpg\" alt=\"Barton Stone Hays – Grapes and Peaches with an Apple\" width=\"300\" height=\"250\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;max-width: 200px;display: 